{"tid":311228,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"欲摸如廁健碩男判守行為 中國博士生指報道令他生活受困","createTime":"2017-07-06T12:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T09:09:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"904b2c8567cf5d46900470ed4c25fa5cc39252e7","tid":311228,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:24:51.000Z","msg":"2017年07月06日<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499314318_85d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F1499314318_85d5.jpg&h=888b4753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來自中國、獲頒獎學金的理大物流及航運學系博士男生，去年進入紅磡一個公廁，要求摸身型健碩、正在小解的男子，更將手伸向對方。對方即拳打博士生，打鬥聲驚動途人通知巡警。警員到場發現博士生受傷，一度以襲擊罪拘捕事主，經一番調查後以遊蕩引致他人擔心罪拘控博士生。案件原定今日開審，博士生最終獲准自簽500元，守行為一年。裁判官警告他要遵守法例，不要再在公眾地方遊蕩。<br />\n<br />\n暫委裁判官馬漢璋指出，香港是開放及公平社會，法律容許同性成年人有親密行為，但必須是雙方同意才可。他叮囑被告不要再犯法，若再犯必會被刑事檢控。被告向裁判官表示，他希望傳媒的報道能公正些，因之前的報道令他生活受到很大困擾，裁判官聞言反問被告：「你有冇反省過（傳媒報道）同你嘅行為有關？」最後叮囑被告：「第一件事，自己反省，咁就唔會有咁多麻煩！」<br />\n操普通話的劉淑利(28歲)報稱理大學生，他被控於去年10月27日紅磡鶴園街公廁4樓男廁內犯案，辯方指被告唸運輸經濟學並獲頒獎學金，預計在2019年完成課程。<br />\n據悉，被告擁有良好背景，事主亦不反對以守行為方式處理案件，考慮上述因素後被告獲撤控並以簽保守行為處理案件。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170706/56920597\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170706%2F56920597&d=1Yex6I4Ej0n%2FmToe9nq7BAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=a9a51584\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170706%2F56920597&h=9f61c132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170706/56920597</a>"},{"pid":"bc1ad73e74700e0d3626f792532e13649db9d1c0","tid":311228,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:26:21.000Z","msg":"this"},{"pid":"dfa24e2f567a9599a3cb250a84079c5817d16f69","tid":311228,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1a5aecfb6646169fbacc3cdd2333ec8d212ae3","tid":311228,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:02:25.000Z","msg":"係支那出手已經死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce8a47b27b4a6a3be5c3c9bc56699610790a6b6","tid":311228,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05be3bd1d6ffc7280a325e914037dab8d09fbf2a","tid":311228,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T07:59:53.000Z","msg":"真係有樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e3bf714be51f365f6a8a7b8e027b0784d3ccb4","tid":311228,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bccb5cc3f515b6ed7c69b02b2044aec05243ba","tid":311228,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"來自中國、獲頒獎學金的理大物流及航運學系博士男生<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}